## 📋 标准来源

### 核心标准

- **[Google SRE Book](https://sre.google/books/)** - Google SRE 书籍
- **[The DevOps Handbook](https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/the-devops-handbook/9781457191381/)** - DevOps 手册
- **[Accelerate](https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/accelerate/9781484203033/)** - 加速：精益软件与 DevOps 的科学
- **[Microsoft DevOps](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/devops/)** - Microsoft DevOps

### 行业最佳实践

- **Continuous Integration (CI)** - 持续集成
- **Continuous Delivery (CD)** - 持续交付
- **Infrastructure as Code (IaC)** - 基础设施即代码
- **Monitoring & Observability** - 监控与可观测性
- **Incident Management** - 事件管理

---

## 🔄 持续集成 (CI)

### CI 流程

```markdown
### 代码提交
1. 开发者提交代码
2. 触发 CI 流水线
3. 代码质量检查

### 构建阶段
1. 依赖安装
2. 代码编译
3. 单元测试
4. 代码覆盖率

### 验证阶段
1. 集成测试
2. E2E 测试
3. 安全扫描
4. 性能测试

### 制品管理
1. 构建 Docker 镜像
2. 推送到镜像仓库
3. 生成版本标签
```

### GitHub Actions 配置

```yaml
# .github/workflows/ci.yml
name: CI Pipeline

on:
  push:
    branches: [main, develop]
  pull_request:
    branches: [main]

jobs:
  lint:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      
      - name: Set up Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v2
        with:
          python-version: 3.11
      
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: |
          python -m pip install --upgrade pip
          pip install -r requirements.txt
          pip install pylint black flake8 mypy
      
      - name: Run linters
        run: |
          black --check app/
          flake8 app/
          pylint app/
          mypy app/
  
  test:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    services:
      postgres:
        image: postgres:15
        env:
          POSTGRES_PASSWORD: test
        options: >-
          --health-cmd pg_isready
          --health-interval 10s
          --health-timeout 5s
          --health-retries 5
        ports:
          - 5432:5432
    
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      
      - name: Set up Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v2
        with:
          python-version: 3.11
      
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: |
          python -m pip install --upgrade pip
          pip install -r requirements.txt
      
      - name: Run tests
        env:
          DATABASE_URL: postgresql://postgres:test@localhost:5432/test
        run: |
          pytest tests/ --cov=app --cov-report=xml
      
      - name: Upload coverage
        uses: codecov/codecov-action@v2
        with:
          file: ./coverage.xml
  
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    needs: [lint, test]
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      
      - name: Set up Docker Buildx
        uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v1
      
      - name: Login to Docker Hub
        uses: docker/login-action@v1
        with:
          username: ${{ secrets.DOCKER_USERNAME }}
          password: ${{ secrets.DOCKER_PASSWORD }}
      
      - name: Build and push
        uses: docker/build-push-action@v2
        with:
          context: .
          push: true
          tags: |
            myapp:${{ github.sha }}
            myapp:latest
```

